subject: Soccer
World Cup 2014 (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Visiting Sweden staged an amazing comeback to earn a 4-4 draw with Germany, scoring four goals in the final 30 minutes in their World Cup qualifying match Tuesday in Berlin.
